Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.29,0:24:19.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is the last person you want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.15,0:24:20.83,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS DRAMA IS FICTION
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.02,0:24:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,HULU ORIGINAL STORY WILL BE RELEASED!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.49,0:24:25.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to go to the\Nperson you love the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.75,0:24:29.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- it's what you wish for, isn't it?\N- Mom, dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.36,0:24:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,NO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.39,0:24:34.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- I want to get married.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.85,0:24:37.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Dear Yoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.42,0:24:42.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine my life without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.49,0:24:47.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you continue to cut my hair?
